        "type": "text",
        "content": "In EDIT mode, the table selected is displayed one display line"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "per row with each field flush left in its respective column."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "Field names or 'TEXT' are presented as column headers. Column"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "widths are determined by the widest value."
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "In Table Edit you can:"
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
        "type": "text",
        "content": "\u0007  Insert a new row with the 'I' command."
      },
      {
        "type": "blank"
      },
      {
